  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Sengoku Logic!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sengoku Logic is a drawing puzzle game where players build famous castles from the Sengoku Period (Warring States period) in Japan. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this title, Kumamoto Castle, said to be the most impregnable castle in Japan, appears!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please give it a try!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drawing puzzle with clues in numbers!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras/a5be02dea707c49a14df34cbe31a54ab.avif?t=1735087710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras_big/a5be02dea707c49a14df34cbe31a54ab.avif?t=1735087710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start from an empty stone wall.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras/c9ab7d5037a98b5b756b7edd6b820d32.avif?t=1735087710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras_big/c9ab7d5037a98b5b756b7edd6b820d32.avif?t=1735087710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buildings appear when you select a stage and complete the puzzle!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras/e8b6dab86cb91a9cebc4972a01978b5a.avif?t=1735087710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras_big/e8b6dab86cb91a9cebc4972a01978b5a.avif?t=1735087710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recreate a castle fortress from the Sengoku Period (Warring States period) !</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras/58d128a25e40637d60855772e9a7fd35.avif?t=1735087710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras_big/58d128a25e40637d60855772e9a7fd35.avif?t=1735087710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the intricate castle at your leisure!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras/2948c89522f47498bfeebbe514b6add9.avif?t=1735087710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras_big/2948c89522f47498bfeebbe514b6add9.avif?t=1735087710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dramatic movie mode and clock mode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras/86404028a891fe891bf545acdf8bd82d.avif?t=1735087710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras_big/86404028a891fe891bf545acdf8bd82d.avif?t=1735087710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy Japanese castles!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Sengoku Logic!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sengoku Logic is a drawing puzzle game where players build famous castles from the Sengoku Period (Warring States period) in Japan. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this title, Kumamoto Castle, said to be the most impregnable castle in Japan, appears!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please give it a try!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drawing puzzle with clues in numbers!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras/a5be02dea707c49a14df34cbe31a54ab.avif?t=1735087710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras_big/a5be02dea707c49a14df34cbe31a54ab.avif?t=1735087710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start from an empty stone wall.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras/c9ab7d5037a98b5b756b7edd6b820d32.avif?t=1735087710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras_big/c9ab7d5037a98b5b756b7edd6b820d32.avif?t=1735087710 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buildings appear when you select a stage and complete the puzzle!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras/e8b6dab86cb91a9cebc4972a01978b5a.avif?t=1735087710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889040/extras_big/e8b6dab86cb91a9cebc4972a01978b5a.avif?t=173508771